reviews.content: Works well in combination with the built-in SSH server provided by checkra1n. Occasionally has an issue where after connecting with an SSH client and entering my password, it won’t send any more data but won’t close the connection.
Works on : iPadPro 12.9 1st gen, iOS 14.2.0, checkra1n 0.12.1
